metadata.name: Happy Accidents
metadata.description:
Happy Accidents is a satirical view or  meme on a similar quote by one of my favorite artist Mr. Ross.

Watching him paint would always put me Zen-like meditative state that made me receive only the good vibes, and I believe thousands of people felt the same. I think if he were still with us, he would have big laugh seeing this meme. 

Part of profits will be donated to Artist Foundation.

Thank you.
